        <abstract> 
<p>CD had intended to pay costs of publishing <hi rend="italic">Movement in plants</hi> because he did not think it fair that Murray should risk publishing a purely scientific work. He would certainly prefer publishing on the usual terms if JM decided to do so. The book contains much new and curious matter, but there are very few persons in England interested in physiological botany.</p> 
        </abstract>
